name: fetch-ponyfill

scripts.build: rimraf build && mkdirp build && node build.js > build/fetch-browser.js
scripts.pretest:browserify: npm run build && browserify tests/fetch-browser.spec.js --outfile build/browser-test-bundle.js
scripts.pretest:webpack: npm run build && webpack --mode development tests/fetch-browser.spec.js -o build/browser-test-bundle.js
